11. Intersectionality of Failure Modes via Global Sensitivity Analysis

Failure modes in neural interfaces are not independent; they exhibit complex coupling that amplifies degradation. We model this intersectionality using Sobol' sensitivity indices.

11.1 Coupled Failure Cascade

