$S_d$ 0.22 Dynamic mismatch alone explains 22% of variance.
$S_{sd}$ (interaction) 0.41 The interaction between structural and dynamic mismatches explains 41% of variance.
$S_{Ts}$ 0.63 Total effect of structural mismatch is 63%.
$S_{Td}$ 0.68 Total effect of dynamic mismatch is 68%.

